normal; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">This magical photographic technique, invented in the mid-nineteenth was pioneered by English Botanist Anna Atkins. For this collection Invincible été pays tribute to the history of Cyanotype to create herbaria precisely reflecting all the magical details of nature.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1679580860695" data-id="1679580860695"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711372621213" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1711372621213" data-resolution="3000x3000" style="display: block;"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/clairefontaine-la-vie-en-vosges" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/336479ee-7945-45b9-b7e3-ada8aecbaa25/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/sq-en-vie-en-vosges.jpg" alt="Clairefontaine La Vie En Vosges" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="500" height="500" natural-width="500" natural-height="500" data-lg-size="3000x3000" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711372621188" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711372621188"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><a href="/collections/clairefontaine-la-vie-en-vosges" class="">La Vie En Vosges</a></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711374169055" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711374169055"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm